spec_data.Name: mingw64-SDL2_mixer
spec_data.Description:
A simple multi-channel audio mixer for SDL2. It supports 4 channels of
16 bit stereo audio, plus a single channel of music, mixed by the popular
MikMod MOD library.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 03:47:59 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: MinGW Windows port of Simple DirectMedia Layer's Sample Mixer Library
